## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="ffa4a-109">アンビエントトランザクションが存在し、<xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Complete%2A> が呼び出された後、トランザクションがロールバックされた場合、<xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> は応答を停止することがあります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ffa4a-109"><xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> may stop responding when there is an ambient transaction and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Complete%2A> is called and afterwards the transaction is rolled back.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ffa4a-110">トランザクションのロールバックが完了する前に <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> が呼び出されると、競合状態が発生し、<xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> の呼び出しが応答を停止します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ffa4a-110">If <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> is called prior to the transaction rollback completing, a race condition will exist, causing the call to <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> to stop responding.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ffa4a-111">これは、次の擬似コードの例で示すことができます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ffa4a-111">This can be illustrated by the following pseudo-code example</span></span>  
  
```  
using (TransactionScope ts = new TransactionScope())   
{  
   try  
   {  
       rc.Complete();  
      ...  
   }  
   Catch (Exception)   
   {  
      rc.Abandon()  
   }  
}  
  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ffa4a-112">これは、<xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext>の操作に推奨されるパターンではありません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ffa4a-112">This is not the recommended pattern for working with <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ffa4a-113">代わりに、try/catch ブロックをトランザクションスコープの外に配置する必要があります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ffa4a-113">Instead the try/catch block should be placed outside of the transaction scope.</span></span>

